sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as User
  participant SPA as React/Vite Public Client
  participant MSAL as MSAL (PKCE)
  participant Entra as Microsoft Entra ID
  participant BFF as BFF (/chat/session)
  participant AES as Agent Execution Service
  participant MCP as MCP Protected API

  User->>SPA: Open app and start chat
  SPA->>MSAL: acquireTokenSilent(scopes)
  alt Cached token available
    MSAL-->>SPA: Access token (sessionStorage cache)
  else Interaction required
    SPA->>MSAL: acquireTokenPopup(scopes)
    MSAL->>Entra: Auth code + PKCE challenge
    Entra-->>MSAL: Authorization code
    MSAL->>Entra: Token exchange + PKCE verifier
    Entra-->>MSAL: Delegated access token
    MSAL-->>SPA: Access token
  end
  SPA->>SPA: Generate traceparent
  SPA->>BFF: POST /chat/session<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>traceparent + {display_name?}
  Note over SPA,BFF: userId/display_name is display-only context, never identity
  Note over SPA,BFF: M7 clients call BFF only (no direct call to Agent Execution Service)
  BFF->>BFF: Validate bearer token (identity source)
  BFF->>AES: Forward request + traceparent
  AES->>MCP: OBO call + traceparent
  MCP-->>AES: Response
  AES-->>BFF: Session payload
  BFF-->>SPA: {session_id, expires_at}
  SPA-->>User: Session ready
